[C406]: [*] Unnecessary list literal (rewrite as a dict literal)
 --> C406.py:1:6
  |
1 | d1 = dict([(1, 2)])
  |      ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ Rewrite as a dict literal
2 | d2 = dict(((1, 2),))
3 | d3 = dict([])
  |

ℹ Unsafe fix
1   |-d1 = dict([(1, 2)])
  1 |+d1 = {1: 2}
2 2 | d2 = dict(((1, 2),))
3 3 | d3 = dict([])
4 4 | d4 = dict(())

[C406]: [*] Unnecessary tuple literal (rewrite as a dict literal)
 --> C406.py:2:6
  |
1 | d1 = dict([(1, 2)])
2 | d2 = dict(((1, 2),))
  |      ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ Rewrite as a dict literal
3 | d3 = dict([])
4 | d4 = dict(())
  |

ℹ Unsafe fix
1 1 | d1 = dict([(1, 2)])
2   |-d2 = dict(((1, 2),))
  2 |+d2 = {1: 2,}
3 3 | d3 = dict([])
4 4 | d4 = dict(())
5 5 | d5 = dict()

